<HEADLINE> Arbi, Sun Jun Advance to Semi-finals </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GLASGOW, Scotland, May 30 (Xinhua) -- Defending champion
Heryanto Arbi of Indonesia beat Dane Thomas Stuer-Lauridsen while
China's Sun Jun defeated Peter Gade Christensen Denmark to advance
to the semi-finals of the world badminton championships.
