<P>
BEIRUT -- One Israeli officer was killed on Friday night in an
attack by guerrillas of the pro-Iranian Hezbollah, or Party of
God, in the Israeli self-proclaimed "security zone" in south
Lebanon, security sources said Saturday morning.
</P>
