KUALA LUMPUR -- Foreign ministers of the Association of
Southeast Asian Nations (ASEAN) on Saturday decided at their
special meeting here to admit Myanmar, Cambodia and Laos into the
regional grouping in July this year, Malaysian Foreign Minister
