Atlantic Treaty Organization (NATO), Assistant Secretary of
Defense Franklin D. Kramer said in an interview with Xinhua at the
Pentagon on Friday. He said that he anticipated the U.S.-Russian
relations "will be good" despite differences between them on NATO
enlargement. 
